{"tid":990152,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"東京地鐵送美食誘乘客提早出門　愈多人參與食物可升級","createTime":"2019-01-21T11:20:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-21T11:25:12.000Z","uid":75969,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9566053706cd70299fcb187e3091679a67498e15","tid":990152,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T11:20:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190121/s00005/601cc8fcbf63a8cd4352b6f477f3f8df.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190121%2Fs00005%2F601cc8fcbf63a8cd4352b6f477f3f8df.jpg&h=7578968b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不少大都市的地鐵系統，如今都面對人滿之患，日本東京亦不例外。為了吸引通勤族改變出行習慣，東京地鐵想出奇招，宣布會向提早出門的乘客送上美食，多人參與的話，得到的美食更會升級。<br />\n<br />\n東京地鐵每天有720萬人次使用，早晚繁忙時間不時出現猶如擠迫沙甸魚的情况。其中連接東京都中野區和千葉縣船橋市的東西線是重災區，每天早上7時50分至8時50分，有超過7.6萬人使用該線，超出容量一倍。<br />\n<br />\n該線新近宣布，未來兩星期每天早上繁忙時間前乘車的2000名乘客，將可各獲贈天婦羅一客，如果有2500人參與，各人將可獲得一客蕎麥麵；如果參與者達3000人或以上，各人將可得到天婦羅和蕎麥麵各一客。<br />\n<br />\n東京都政府未來兩星期亦會推出措施，鼓勵分散通勤人流，有近1000家企業參與，包括容許僱員提早上下班時間，甚至在家工作。<br />\n<br />\n（法新社）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/國際/article/20190121/s00005/1548067478517/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%2Farticle%2F20190121%2Fs00005%2F1548067478517%2F&d=6to3LhKkOqiXgU6uSObXnTQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=83bf993b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%2Farticle%2F20190121%2Fs00005%2F1548067478517%2F&h=f5b4f179\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/國際/article/20190121/s00005/1548067478517/</a>"},{"pid":"a7954d76940d04faea662c511fb5b8a3fcbb20e1","tid":990152,"uid":152047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T11:21:50.000Z","msg":"應該好有效<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2accac00aea905cb9138da223fa932faa04b2a33","tid":990152,"uid":129521,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T11:23:23.000Z","msg":"我寧願瞓多陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c10e641e9d3431ee11bd283a6eb6ac2c821421d","tid":990152,"uid":40932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a7954d76940d04faea662c511fb5b8a3fcbb20e1","tid":990152,"uid":152047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T11:21:50.000Z","msg":"應該好有效<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T11:24:27.000Z","msg":"攞既都係支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed945e0f54a94a6bfe36f85e77b33fbe19d5580b","tid":990152,"uid":81518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T11:25:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}